- Jock Goddard. - Adam Cassidy.

556
00:37:17,040 --> 00:37:19,272
原来就是你啊 一切都还行？
Of course you are. Everything all right?

557
00:37:19,272 --> 00:37:20,089
安顿得如何？
Settling in OK?

558
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:22,083
