Oh, yeah, it's beautiful. Thank you.

560
00:37:24,022 --> 00:37:25,210
很好 我们开始吧
- Good. Let's get started.

561
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:26,521
好的
OK.

562
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:30,085
先生 我认为你把X型用于…
