567
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:45,405
会议室里所有人都收到了电邮
Everyone I sent an e-mail to is in this room.

568
00:37:45,405 --> 00:37:46,242
除了一人
Except for one.

569
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:52,122
现代战争还是无法避免被友方误伤
Death by friendly fire remains a sad reality of war.

570
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:55,568
