Yes. 'Cause in the heat of battle

575
00:38:06,221 --> 00:38:07,247
它会有不俗的表现
that can be the difference

576
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:10,165
命悬杀死敌人或者…
between killing the enemy or...

577
