Hi, Adam. I'm calling from Jock Goddard's office.

600
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:28,806
乔克先生邀请部分客人光临他在汉普顿的家
Jock is having a few people over to his house in the Hamptons

601
00:39:28,960 --> 00:39:31,361
时间是星期六 他希望你也来
on Saturday and he'd like you to join him.

602
00:39:38,160 --> 00:39:40,208
目前已申请军方资助了
So now we go for military funding.

603
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:43,284
好极了 祝贺你
Dude, that's great. Congratulations, man.

604
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:47,367
我有一事相求
Hey, so, I got a favor to ask.

605
00:39:49,400 --> 00:39:51,562
我下周要到艾康公司面试
I got an interview at Eikon next week.

606
00:39:53,040 --> 00:39:56,408
也许我的简历会成为故纸推中的一张
And I know I'm gonna be another resume in a stack

607
00:39:56,560 --> 00:39:58,722
除非我有闪光点
if I don't build some traction.

608
00:40:00,400 --> 00:40:02,368
对
Right.

609
00:40:03,680 --> 00:40:06,809
很难为情 不过…
So, I feel awkward even asking you this, but...

610
00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:08,644
别担心
Hey, of course.

611
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:10,729
周一我会和人事部打招呼的
All right, I'll speak to HR on Monday.

612
00:40:11,720 --> 00:40:13,370
放心吧
All right.

613
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:15,200
多谢
Thanks.

614
00:41:09,160 --> 00:41:10,321
那家伙人还不错
Nicest guy.

615
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:14,087
闯红灯追尾我的车
Right through the red light and hit the back of the car.

616
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:16,328
- 诚恳的道歉  - 有人破财了
- Very apologetic. - Somebody looks lost.

617
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:21,329
- 他来了  - 很高兴你能来
- There he is. - I'm glad you could make it.

618
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:24,324
- 谢谢你的邀请 戈达先生  - 叫我乔克
- Thanks for having me, Mr. Goddard. - Jock.

619
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:26,130
你认识汤姆的 对吧
You know Tom, of course.

620
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:28,828
乔克告诉我说股票升值了
Jock tells me my stock's gone up in value

621
00:41:28,828 --> 00:41:30,285
因为你对X型的定位
since your Type X pitch.

622
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:33,033
上场第一击就爆掉了计分牌
First time up at bat and you bang it off the scoreboard?

623
00:41:33,033 --> 00:41:33,489
就该这么干
Way to go.

624
00:41:33,640 --> 00:41:36,086
这是艾玛 负责我们的…
And this is Emma. She's spearheading the marketing

625
00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:38,720
新Occura智能手机市场工作
on our new smartphone, Occura.

626
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:40,325
西装不错
Nice suit.

627
00:41:40,480 --> 00:41:41,731
别小看她
Watch our for her.

628
00:41:41,731 --> 00:41:44,565
她可是普林斯顿常青藤大学的高材生哟
She's one of those Ivy Leaguers. Princeton.

629
00:41:44,720 --> 00:41:46,324
应该是耶鲁大学吧？
Yale, actually.

630
00:41:46,520 --> 00:41:48,329
她兄弟们也念耶鲁大学
Where her brothers went.

631
00:41:48,520 --> 00:41:51,126
你怎么知道我是耶鲁的？
How did you know I went to Yale?

632
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:53,891
脸书或是别的地方听说的
It was on Facebook or something.

633
00:41:56,200 --> 00:41:58,328
毫无隐私啊
So much for privacy.

634
00:41:58,480 --> 00:42:02,371
隐私 现在已经是种笑话了
Privacy. Absolute myth, no such thing.

635
00:42:02,520 --> 00:42:04,602
- 汤姆 想喝一杯吗？  - 当然
- Tom, you want a drink? - Yeah, absolutely.

636
00:42:07,720 --> 00:42:09,051
白葡萄酒 先生？
A glass of wine, sir?

637
00:42:09,200 --> 00:42:11,089
- 白葡萄酒  - 我要冰矿泉水
- White wine. - Mineral water, cold.

638
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:14,124
待会见
See you later.

639
00:42:16,640 --> 00:42:19,246
有点像波尔多 太干了
Kind of like a Bordeaux, more dry.

640
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:32,966
如果你在找卫生间 走过头了
if you're looking for the bathroom, you missed it.

641
00:43:34,720 --> 00:43:37,087
不好意思 …
Yeah, sorry, I, uh...

642
00:43:37,320 --> 00:43:39,448
我看到那个收音机  还能用吗？
I saw the radio. Does it work?

643
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:43,207
还能用 全都能用 我做的
Yeah, they work. They all work. I built them.

644
00:43:43,360 --> 00:43:46,887
十多岁时的癖好 火腿一族(业余无线电)
That's how I spent my teens. Ham radio.

645
00:43:47,040 --> 00:43:48,610
你在哪儿长大？
Where'd you grow up?

646
00:43:49,680 --> 00:43:52,889
汉米尔顿 人口约3500人
Town of Hamilton, 3500 people.

647
00:43:53,040 --> 00:43:55,202
那是哪里？
Where is that?

648
00:43:56,640 --> 00:43:58,165
不值一提
It doesn't matter.

649
00:44:03,080 --> 00:44:05,112
你让我想起怀特公司
You remind me of Wyatt.

650
00:44:05,112 --> 00:44:07,483
非常吃惊他们居然放你走
I'm surprised he let you go.

651
00:44:07,640 --> 00:44:09,483
他对我不甚感兴趣
He wasn't too happy about it.

652
00:44:09,640 --> 00:44:12,962
我知道有一天他们会成为我的强力竞争对手
I knew he'd be my competition someday.

653
00:44:13,120 --> 00:44:15,088
我在他意识到之前就意识到了
I knew it before he did.

654
00:44:15,240 --> 00:44:16,924
那你为什么把他收入麾下？
Why'd you take him under your wing?

655
00:44:17,080 --> 00:44:19,481
与他个人无关 事关开发产品…
It's not about him. It's about putting products out there

656
00:44:19,640 --> 00:44:21,768
能让人们生活的更好
to make people's lives better.

657
00:44:21,920 --> 00:44:23,968
竞争推动创新
Competition fuels innovation.

658
00:44:24,120 --> 00:44:26,487
否则就没有艾康公司的今天
Without it, Eikon wouldn't be where it is today.

659
00:44:26,680 --> 00:44:28,489
现在发展到什么阶段了？
And where is that?

660
00:44:29,680 --> 00:44:32,650
革命前夜
On the eve of a revolution.

661
00:44:38,080 --> 00:44:39,889
你儿子吗？
Is that your son?

662
00:44:41,160 --> 00:44:43,640
是的 迪兰
Yeah, that's Dylan.

663
00:44:44,680 --> 00:44:46,682
人一旦有点成功 就会觉得自己…
You have a bit of success, you begin to think

664
00:44:46,840 --> 00:44:51,209
能左右一些事情 但…
that you've got some control over things, but...

665
00:44:52,240 --> 00:44:55,528
…天往往不遂人愿
...shit happens to everybody.

666
00:44:55,680 --> 00:44:58,251
是啊
Yeah.

667
00:45:03,360 --> 00:45:05,647
我7岁时丧母
I lost my mother when I was seven.

668
00:45:08,520 --> 00:45:10,648
你还记得她吗？
Do you remember her?

669
00:45:12,160 --> 00:45:13,924
不太记得了
Not much.

670
00:45:15,080 --> 00:45:17,560
我感觉她逐渐离我远去
I feel like I lose her a little more every day.

671
00:45:17,720 --> 00:45:19,245
对
Yeah.

672
00:45:20,840 --> 00:45:22,569
迪兰死后的很多夜晚
Couple nights after Dilly died,

673
00:45:22,720 --> 00:45:25,690
我常在夜晚痛醒
I woke up in the middle of the night in a panic.

674
00:45:26,720 --> 00:45:29,166
翻遍整个房子 他的整个房间…
Rummaged through the whole house, his whole room...

675
00:45:30,560 --> 00:45:32,688
…试图找到一点慰籍
...looking for anything.

676
00:45:34,720 --> 00:45:37,690
孩提的涂鸦画 作业本…
Kid's drawings, schoolwork...

677
00:45:39,200 --> 00:45:40,929
…旧网球鞋
...old pair of tennis shoes.

678
00:45:41,080 --> 00:45:45,051
一切能回忆起他的东西
Anything that would keep him alive.

679
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:51,765
在前厅楼梯口
The front hall, under the stairs.

680
00:45:54,960 --> 00:45:56,325
什么先生？
Sir?

681
00:45:58,560 --> 00:46:00,767
卫生间
The bathroom.

682
00:46:02,640 --> 00:46:04,165
谢谢
Thanks.

683
00:46:15,636 --> 00:46:16,178
（米彻姆：继续等待）

684
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:20,049
你的西装也没那么差劲啦
You know, the suit's not all that bad.

685
00:46:20,200 --> 00:46:22,601
你不用藏在这里
You don't have to hide way out here.

686
00:46:22,800 --> 00:46:25,883
我这是欲擒故纵
I was, uh, playing hard to get.

687
00:46:26,040 --> 00:46:28,691
显然你得手了
But you're already gotten.

688
00:46:30,640 --> 00:46:32,927
告诉我
So tell me,

689
00:46:33,080 --> 00:46:34,684
你怎么会了解我那么多事
how is it that you know so much about me

690
00:46:34,840 --> 00:46:37,764
而我却对你一无所知？
and I know nothing about you?

691
00:46:41,560 --> 00:46:44,609
我祖母住的是一个小房间
It's this, uh, little row home my grandmother owned.

692
00:46:44,760 --> 00:46:46,808
五个人共用洗手间
Five of us sharing one bathroom.

693
00:46:46,960 --> 00:46:49,531
我爸爸曾是保安
My dad was a security guard.

694
00:46:49,680 --> 00:46:52,650
现在患有肺气肿 但还在吸烟
Now he has emphysema, but still smokes.

695
00:46:52,800 --> 00:46:55,610
我敢肯定他把烟藏在护士那儿
And I'm pretty sure he's putting it to the nurse I'm paying for.

696
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:02,367
每当我想到要失去他…
When I think of losing him...

697
00:47:07,280 --> 00:47:08,645
你呢？
What about you?

698
00:47:11,560 --> 00:47:13,847
我家教严格…
I come from a family where...

699
00:47:14,840 --> 00:47:16,191
家里期望过高
the expectation is so high

700
00:47:16,191 --> 00:47:17,844
我真的难以达成
that I can't really ever succeed.

701
00:47:19,880 --> 00:47:23,248
好在我一直有努力
It's fine, it's just that I keep trying.

702
00:47:31,440 --> 00:47:33,010
那么…
So...

703
00:47:34,000 --> 00:47:36,810
我想一路睡到高层
I'm trying to sleep my way to the top.

704
00:47:38,720 --> 00:47:40,802
地下恋情么？
Are we covered?

705
00:47:44,200 --> 00:47:47,443
得了 带我回家？
Come on. Take me home?

706
00:47:47,600 --> 00:47:49,568
好
Yeah.

707
00:51:04,280 --> 00:51:05,805
爸爸？
Dad?

708
00:51:07,880 --> 00:51:10,326
有客人来
You got a visitor.

709
00:51:16,760 --> 00:51:18,364
你是谁？
Who are you?

710
00:51:18,520 --> 00:51:22,206
你应该扣掉手机电池
You might want to remove the battery from your cellular device.

711
00:51:23,080 --> 00:51:25,321
什么？
What?

712
00:51:25,480 --> 00:51:27,202
别以为你没在通话状态
You think 'cause you're not on a call,

713
00:51:27,202 --> 00:51:28,086
他们就听不到你
they can't hear you?

714
00:51:29,920 --> 00:51:31,490
探员甘布
Agent Gamble.

715
00:51:32,960 --> 00:51:35,247
FBI犯罪调查科
I'm with the FBI's Criminal Investigation Division.

716
00:51:41,080 --> 00:51:44,163
我们调查怀特公司有五年了
We've been looking at the Wyatt Corp for about five years now.

717
00:51:45,120 --> 00:51:47,566
- 我不在怀特公司工作  - 约翰·摩尔是怀特员工
- I don't work for Wyatt. - John Moore did.

