Don't bullshit me.

728
00:52:23,000 --> 00:52:24,968
好的 我想你可以走了
OK, I think it's time for you to go.

729
00:52:25,160 --> 00:52:27,288
你以为怀特会给你一大笔钱然后让你安然离开？
You think Wyatt's gonna fill your pockets and let you walk?

730
00:52:27,440 --> 00:52:28,965
我不知道你在说什么
I don't know what you're talking about, OK?

731
00:52:29,160 --> 00:52:31,561
别这样 亚当
Come on, Adam.

732
00:52:31,720 --> 00:52:33,722
你以为你还能挺多久？
How long do you think you can keep this up?

733
00:52:35,640 --> 00:52:38,610
只要一个过失 你立马就玩完
All it takes is one mistake, one slip up.

734
00:52:42,840 --> 00:52:44,126
对不起 我帮不了你
I'm sorry, I can't help you.

735
00:52:47,920 --> 00:52:51,003
别追悔莫及
Just don't wait till it's too late.

736
00:53:17,400 --> 00:53:20,404
你不打算告诉我发生什么事了吗？
You wanna tell me what's going on?

737
00:53:23,920 --> 00:53:25,285
你不懂的
You wouldn't understand.

738
00:53:26,520 --> 00:53:28,807
我以前太匆忙
Yeah, I was probably too busy

739
00:53:28,960 --> 00:53:31,691
每天供你三餐
putting three meals in front of you every day

740
00:53:31,840 --> 00:53:34,650
给你别人都有的父母之爱
and giving you all the love that parents had.

741
00:53:35,640 --> 00:53:39,122
亚当 我们会过得幸福的
Come on, Adam. We had a perfect life.

742
00:53:39,320 --> 00:53:42,085
如果花在你身上的保险有一半能用在妈妈…
You know, if your insurance covered even half of what morn needed...

743
00:53:42,280 --> 00:53:43,440
别和病魔斗争
Don't try to revise death.

744
00:53:43,440 --> 00:53:44,601
不然你希望我怎么样？
What did you want me to do?

745
00:53:44,760 --> 00:53:46,728
我希望你斗争
I wanted you to fight.

746
00:53:46,880 --> 00:53:49,042
我想我们至少能给妈一次机会
I wanted us to have enough to at least give her a chance.

747
00:53:49,240 --> 00:53:51,049
但你却放弃了
You gotta give that up.

748
00:53:52,280 --> 00:53:53,814
这些公司把财富都偷走了
These companies steal so much,

749
00:53:53,814 --> 00:53:55,250
不剩一点
there's nothing left to earn.

750
00:53:55,400 --> 00:53:57,880
你的所为也没有什么成效
Yeah, what you're doing doesn't make it right.

751
00:53:58,040 --> 00:54:00,088
没有
No.

752
00:54:00,240 --> 00:54:02,447
没有人能绝对正确
No one can make it right.

753
00:54:02,600 --> 00:54:05,763
我为什么不能得到属于自己的一份？
So, why shouldn't I get my share? Huh?

754
00:54:07,440 --> 00:54:10,922
FBI刚从我们家离开
The FBI just walked out of our house.

755
00:54:11,080 --> 00:54:13,367
我不想跟你一样的人生
I don't want to end up like you.

756
00:54:54,920 --> 00:54:56,809
原来乔克是这个想法
So that's what he's up to.

757
00:54:58,520 --> 00:55:00,204
你要的都齐了
That's what you wanted.

758
00:55:01,360 --> 00:55:03,328
任务完成 卑鄙的我
I'm done now. This isn't who I am.

759
00:55:03,480 --> 00:55:07,280
你本性如此 搜过他身没有？
This is exactly who you are. Did you frisk him?

760
00:55:10,280 --> 00:55:12,123
你有所隐藏？
You hiding something?

761
00:55:14,320 --> 00:55:15,924
住手！
Knock it Off!

762
00:55:16,120 --> 00:55:18,691
你最近内心有点波澜吧？
You've been a little temperamental lately, haven't you?

763
00:55:18,840 --> 00:55:20,251
你爱上那女人了？
Are you falling for that girl?

764
00:55:20,400 --> 00:55:23,643
- 他爱上的是乔克  - 好了 好了！
- He's falling for Jock. - All right, all right!

765
00:55:26,800 --> 00:55:28,245
他说什么了？
What'd he talk about?

766
00:55:28,400 --> 00:55:31,802
他谈到科技进步 丰富了人们的生活
He talked about progress, enriching people's lives.

767
00:55:31,960 --> 00:55:34,122
谈到他儿子了吗？
Yeah, he talk about his son?

768
00:55:34,280 --> 00:55:36,203
说了一点
Yeah. A little.

769
00:55:36,960 --> 00:55:38,928
是不是很耳熟？
It seem rehearsed?

770
00:55:39,080 --> 00:55:40,161
不
No.

771
00:55:40,320 --> 00:55:43,403
我早就说了
It did the first time he told it.

772
00:55:43,560 --> 00:55:45,881
当全世界都爱上乔克·戈达的时候
That was when the world fell in love with Jock Goddard,

773
00:55:46,040 --> 00:55:48,168
痛不欲生的父亲
the grieving father.

774
00:55:48,360 --> 00:55:53,571
幸好因为他儿子的噩耗拯救了艾康公司
That story of his little dead boy saved Eikon.

775
00:55:53,720 --> 00:55:55,609
我已经拿到你想要的 懂吗？
I got what you asked for, OK?

776
00:55:55,760 --> 00:55:57,205
我们有约在先 我只想拿到我的钱
We had a deal. I just want my money.

777
00:55:57,360 --> 00:55:59,328
他想拿份内钱
Oh, he wants his money.

778
00:55:59,480 --> 00:56:00,832
钱我们暂时替你保管
We'll keep your money for you.

779
00:56:00,832 --> 00:56:02,404
你还得更进一步
You'll be doing five to ten upstate.

780
00:56:02,560 --> 00:56:04,324
我已经按约定拿到了规格书 说好的
I got the specs. That was the deal.

781
00:56:04,480 --> 00:56:06,608
光有图片还不够好
Pictures are no good to me.

782
00:56:06,800 --> 00:56:07,979
我需要知道是什么情况
I need to know what it does,

783
00:56:07,979 --> 00:56:09,770
我想要的是把它拿在手里 看实际运行效果！
I need to hold it in my hand and see it run!

784
00:56:09,920 --> 00:56:12,207
听懂了没有 必须拿到我手里！
Do you understand me? Put it in my fucking hand!

785
00:56:12,360 --> 00:56:14,362
不然怎样？ 像理查德一样被终结？
Or what? I end up like Richard?

786
00:56:24,040 --> 00:56:26,611
乔克负责建立原型体
Jock builds one prototype.

787
00:56:27,520 --> 00:56:30,168
各部件的组装都在研发中心密室进行
It's assembled in the vault, piece by piece,

788
00:56:30,168 --> 00:56:32,242
直到验收测试
until beta trials.

789
00:56:32,400 --> 00:56:34,482
这间密室位于第38层
It stays in the vault on the 38th floor.

790
00:56:34,640 --> 00:56:37,246
没有文件 没有源码 你什么也…
Without files, without source code, you can't do...

791
00:56:37,400 --> 00:56:39,880
不 我不需要他的文件
No, I don't need his files.

792
00:56:40,920 --> 00:56:42,649
我只需看到他的思想原型
I just need to see his vision.

793
00:56:42,800 --> 00:56:46,386
不 我不干了
No, I'm not doing this anymore.

794
00:56:46,386 --> 00:56:47,283
我退出
I'm out.

795
00:56:50,320 --> 00:56:54,245
你退出？ 孩子 等我说你可以退出的时候
You're out? You are only out, my son,

796
00:56:54,400 --> 00:56:57,244
你才能退出
when I say you're out!

797
00:56:57,400 --> 00:56:59,448
你现在受我胁迫
I own you right now.

798
00:56:59,640 --> 00:57:03,281
明白吗？一切尽在我的掌握
You see? I can get to anyone.

799
00:57:06,280 --> 00:57:09,170
别把事情复杂化
Don't make this harder than it has to be.

800
00:57:10,440 --> 00:57:11,854
生意就是生意 亚当
It's just business, Adam.

801
00:57:11,854 --> 00:57:13,649
每个人都偷窃 每个人都说谎
Everybody steals, everybody lies.

802
00:57:13,800 --> 00:57:16,007
无所谓对错
There's no right or wrong.

803
00:57:16,200 --> 00:57:17,964
只有输和赢
There's just winning or losing.

804
00:57:25,160 --> 00:57:27,662
现在第一步任务
Now the first order of business

805
00:57:27,662 --> 00:57:30,087
是提取艾玛的指纹
is lifting Emma's fingerprints.

806
00:57:34,160 --> 00:57:35,571
我父母最近忙着操办…
So my parents are having this thing

807
00:57:35,760 --> 00:57:38,525
我哥在周末的婚礼
for my brother's engagement this weekend.

808
00:57:38,720 --> 00:57:41,087
要我一起去吗？
You wanna go with me?

809
00:57:43,800 --> 00:57:45,484
拜见父母？
To meet your parents?

810
00:57:45,640 --> 00:57:47,449
吃顿饭而已
It's just dinner and drinks.

811
00:57:49,600 --> 00:57:51,329
你们…
You, uh...

812
00:57:53,640 --> 00:57:56,962
你确定可以和我发展长久关系了？
You sure I'm relationship material?

813
00:57:59,440 --> 00:58:02,649
算了 一起吃饭也挺无聊的
You know what? It's... It's actually gonna be really boring.

814
00:58:02,800 --> 00:58:05,451
你不去也好
Probably better if you don't.

815
00:58:08,040 --> 00:58:10,168
我当然去
Of course I will.

816
00:58:10,320 --> 00:58:12,288
无聊也去？
Even if it is boring?

817
00:58:15,480 --> 00:58:17,801
是 无聊也去
Yeah, even if it's boring.

818
00:58:40,520 --> 00:58:41,965
怎么了你？
Hey, what happened to you?

819
00:58:42,160 --> 00:58:44,288
凯文 你怎么来了？
Kev! What are you doing here?

820
00:58:44,440 --> 00:58:46,363
你以为我在做什么？
What do you think I'm doing here?

821
00:58:47,520 --> 00:58:49,329
对 面试
Your interview. Right.

822
00:58:51,880 --> 00:58:55,123
- 情况如何？ 我和人事部门招呼过了  - 不 你没有
- How'd it go? I spoke to HR. - No, you didn't.

823
00:58:56,120 --> 00:58:57,485
对不起 兄弟 我…
I'm sorry, man. I, uh...

824
00:58:58,520 --> 00:58:59,651
我最近压力很大
I've been under a ton of pressure.

825
00:58:59,651 --> 00:59:00,363
完全忘了…
I completely forgot...

826
00:59:00,520 --> 00:59:01,682
是啊 我理解你
Yeah, I understand, man.

827
00:59:01,682 --> 00:59:03,729
你去了新公司 买新车 有新女朋友
Your new apartment, new car, new girlfriend.

828
00:59:03,880 --> 00:59:05,370
你真不知道我的处境
You have no idea what I'm dealing with.

829
00:59:05,560 --> 00:59:08,530
是 我不知道 这辈子也无法知道了
No, I don't. And I don't think I ever will.

830
00:59:08,680 --> 00:59:10,887
- 谢谢  - 凯文 我真的很抱歉
- Thanks. - Come on, Kev. I'm sorry, man.

831
00:59:11,040 --> 00:59:12,201
凯文！
Kev!

832
00:59:12,400 --> 00:59:14,243
戈达先生想见你
Mr. Goddard wants to see you.

833
00:59:16,760 --> 00:59:19,525
好 我知道的
Yeah, I understand that.

834
00:59:20,560 --> 00:59:22,594
怀特公司必须考虑我方的提议
Wyatt has to consider our offer.

835
00:59:22,594 --> 00:59:23,643
他没的选
He has no choice.

836
00:59:23,800 --> 00:59:26,451
我指的是 他现在像是在泰坦尼克号上跳舞
(马上要完蛋)
I mean, he's tap dancing on the Titanic.

837
00:59:26,600 --> 00:59:29,080
进来吧
Come on in.

838
00:59:29,240 --> 00:59:30,526
有人进来了而已
Look, somebody just walked in.

839
00:59:30,680 --> 00:59:32,409
我有些事务要处理下
I've got something I've got to deal with.

840
00:59:32,560 --> 00:59:34,449
好吧 谢谢
All right. Thanks.

841
00:59:36,240 --> 00:59:39,005
别忘记您在俱乐部预订的午餐
Don't forget, you have a lunch reservation at the club.

842
00:59:39,560 --> 00:59:42,450
我们去兜兜风 顺便请你吃午饭
Come on. Let's take a drive. I'll buy you lunch.

843
00:59:42,640 --> 00:59:46,406
今早收到一些与你有关的新闻
Got some interesting news this morning concerning you.

844
00:59:46,600 --> 00:59:50,571
说给你听之前 我得确认真假
Thought I'd make sure it was true before I talk to you about it.

845
00:59:51,600 --> 00:59:55,127
- 一切还好吧？  - 你说呢
- Is everything all right? - You tell me.

846
00:59:55,320 --> 00:59:59,928
国防部同意投资X型了
The DOD has given us preliminary funding for Type X.

847
01:00:09,520 --> 01:00:12,444
- 就停这里吧 戈达先生  - 谢了 伙计
- We'll leave it here, Mr. Goddard. - Thanks, Bud.

848
01:00:12,600 --> 01:00:15,444
- 觉得怎样？  - 充满了力量
- Well, what do you think? - It's powerful.

849
01:00:15,600 --> 01:00:18,001
没错
Yeah, it is.

850
01:00:18,160 --> 01:00:20,447
算是你拯救X型项目的红利吧
Consider it a loaner for saving Type X.

851
01:00:20,600 --> 01:00:23,444
- 乔克 我不能接受  - 你可以
- Jock, I couldn't. - Yeah, you could.

852
01:00:23,640 --> 01:00:27,008
力量就像果汁 你得习惯饮用它
Power is the juice, get used to drinking it.

853
01:00:28,280 --> 01:00:30,009
我听你谈到Occura
I heard you talking about Occura.

854
01:00:30,160 --> 01:00:31,605
外面有很多疯传
There's a lot of buzz about it.

855
01:00:31,760 --> 01:00:34,730
是的 Occura项目已经待产
Yeah, Occura's been, uh, gestating

856
01:00:34,880 --> 01:00:38,805
这些年来
for... quite a few years.

857
01:00:38,960 --> 01:00:41,486
直到最近我们才能…
We only recently were able to put

858
01:00:41,640 --> 01:00:44,166
把所有的元素组装成实用版本
all of the elements together to make it happen.

859
01:00:44,320 --> 01:00:45,890
- 一杯咖啡  - 一杯水
- I'll have coffee. - I'll have a water.

860
01:00:46,040 --> 01:00:47,121
好的
Very good.

861
01:00:47,280 --> 01:00:50,489
想象外出时除了手机什么都不带
Imagine walking around with nothing but your cell phone.

862
01:00:50,640 --> 01:00:52,961
没有钱包 没有钥匙
No wallet, no keys.

863
01:00:53,120 --> 01:00:54,929
手机可以是数字钱包
Like a digital wallet.

864
01:00:55,080 --> 01:00:57,367
是驾照 是信用卡
It'll be your driver's license, it'll be your credit card,

865
01:00:57,520 --> 01:00:58,487
是很多其它东西
it'll be more than that.

866
01:00:58,640 --> 01:01:00,159
超薄可折叠
Super slim. Foldable,

867
01:01:00,159 --> 01:01:02,645
能自充电
with a battery that recharges itself

868
01:01:02,840 --> 01:01:05,491
只要附近有环境电源
from any ambient electrical source.

869
01:01:05,680 --> 01:01:08,650
它知道你去过哪里 和谁去的
It'll know where you've been, who you've been with.

870
01:01:08,800 --> 01:01:12,691
它能帮你处理轻重缓急 理财
It'll track your priorities, expenditures,

871
01:01:12,840 --> 01:01:15,844
监管身体 日程安排
your health, calendar.

872
01:01:16,000 --> 01:01:18,319
它知道你的全部
It will know who you are.

873
01:01:18,319 --> 01:01:19,925
而它则受我们的控制
And it's all ours.

874
01:01:20,080 --> 01:01:22,481
你真的认为同处一室的人…
You think people really want all that personal information

875
01:01:22,640 --> 01:01:23,801
也会要这样的私人信息？
under one roof?

876
01:01:23,960 --> 01:01:27,009
与同处一室无关 亚当
It's not the roof that matters, Adam.

877
01:01:27,200 --> 01:01:31,444
它提供的是一种家的温暖感觉
It's the warm fuzzy feeling of the home under it.

878
01:01:31,600 --> 01:01:33,577
现在的人都神经兮兮的
People are so distracted these days,

879
01:01:33,577 --> 01:01:35,127
经常连自己是谁都忘了
they don't know who they are.

880
01:01:35,280 --> 01:01:36,520
但我们不会
But we will.

881
01:01:36,680 --> 01:01:39,650
我们甚至比他们自己更了解他们
We'll know them better than they know themselves.

882
01:01:42,400 --> 01:01:44,528
天啊
Oh, my goodness.

883
01:01:53,720 --> 01:01:54,607
乔克
Jock.

884
01:01:54,760 --> 01:01:56,250
尼克
Nick.

885
01:01:56,440 --> 01:01:58,010
多久没见了？
How long has it been?

886
01:01:59,000 --> 01:02:00,923
没多久
Not long enough.

887
01:02:01,080 --> 01:02:03,686
你还是一副一柱擎天的气势
You look like you're holding up all right.

888
01:02:03,840 --> 01:02:07,083
喔 还行 哪阵风把你吹到这儿来的？
Oh, I'm doing fine. What brings you here?

889
01:02:07,280 --> 01:02:09,681
午饭风 午饭风驱使我来的
Lunch. Lunch brings me here.

890
01:02:10,720 --> 01:02:12,563
- 你还记得朱迪斯吗  - 当然
- You remember Judith. - Oh, of course.

891
01:02:12,720 --> 01:02:14,643
- 你好 朱迪斯？  - 还行
- How are you, Judith? - Good.

892
01:02:14,800 --> 01:02:16,263
记得亚当·坎西迪吗？
You remember Adam Cassidy.

893
01:02:16,263 --> 01:02:17,565
是他设计了你的Ethion
He designed your Ethion.

894
01:02:17,720 --> 01:02:19,927
当然是他
