895
01:02:20,840 --> 01:02:22,683
你也好 亚当
Hello, again, Adam.

896
01:02:24,760 --> 01:02:26,569
他让我想起了你
He reminds me of you.

897
01:02:26,760 --> 01:02:29,206
回想当年 你抛弃了我们
Way back when, before you walked out on us.

898
01:02:29,360 --> 01:02:30,725
别颠倒黑白吧
Let's not muddle the facts.

899
01:02:30,880 --> 01:02:32,644
是你赶我走 然后关上我身后的门
You asked me to walk and locked the door behind me.

900
01:02:32,800 --> 01:02:35,531
好在我比亚当聪明点
Besides, I was smarter than Adam here.

901
01:02:35,680 --> 01:02:37,682
我没有浪费时间去拍你的马屁
And I didn't spend all my time kissing your ass.

902
01:02:40,240 --> 01:02:41,453
Ethion项目进展如何？
How is Ethion?

903
01:02:41,453 --> 01:02:44,609
我们有些耳闻
We've heard remarkably little about it.

904
01:02:44,760 --> 01:02:46,454
Ethion项目进展顺利
Ethion's fine.

905
01:02:46,454 --> 01:02:47,923
Occura项目如何？
How's Occura?

906
01:02:48,080 --> 01:02:50,003
计划之中
Right on schedule.

907
01:02:50,200 --> 01:02:52,851
有一点你永远无法复制
And it's something you're never going to be able to duplicate.

908
01:02:53,000 --> 01:02:54,729
是什么？
Is that so?

909
01:02:56,160 --> 01:02:59,209
尼克 记得我们曾经共同创意？
Remember when we used to share ideas, Nick?

910
01:02:59,360 --> 01:03:00,600
我没忘
I try not to.

911
01:03:00,760 --> 01:03:02,493
我俩一起时
When we put our heads together,

912
01:03:02,493 --> 01:03:04,606
没有我们解决不了的问题
there was no problem we couldn't solve.

913
01:03:04,800 --> 01:03:06,404
没有什么我们做不出来的
Nothing we couldn't make.

914
01:03:06,560 --> 01:03:08,608
应该是没什么我解决不了的困难
There was no problem I couldn't solve.

915
01:03:08,800 --> 01:03:10,643
没什么我做不出来的东西
Nothing I couldn't make.

916
01:03:12,320 --> 01:03:14,448
我怀念你的友谊
I miss your friendship.

917
01:03:14,640 --> 01:03:17,405
不如我们什么时候再聚聚
Why don't we sit down together sometime.

918
01:03:19,520 --> 01:03:22,967
你总是满嘴胡言 你坐着就像…
Always so full of shit. You sit here like...

919
01:03:24,040 --> 01:03:26,566
…像个令人仰慕的大亨
...like some big shot with boy wonder here,

920
01:03:26,720 --> 01:03:29,644
用屁股吞云吐雾 搞的煞有介事
blowing smoke up your ass like it's still relevant.

921
01:03:29,800 --> 01:03:32,280
事实是我会埋葬了你
The truth is, I'm gonna bury you,

922
01:03:32,440 --> 01:03:35,967
替你工作的人将会替我工作
and your boy here is gonna be working for me again.

923
01:03:36,160 --> 01:03:40,006
因为替你工作就是替我工作
Because working for you, means he'll be working for me.

924
01:03:42,360 --> 01:03:45,125
别让午餐变冷 尼克
Don't let your lunch get cold, Nick.

925
01:03:54,920 --> 01:03:56,922
很高兴见到你 朱迪斯
Nice seeing you, Judith.

926
01:04:15,840 --> 01:04:18,207
他一遍一遍的查戈达的资料
He's running search after search on Goddard.

927
01:04:20,400 --> 01:04:22,243
他在找什么？
What is he looking for?

928
01:04:22,400 --> 01:04:23,811
我不知道
I don't know.

929
01:04:27,840 --> 01:04:30,605
我觉得这孩子已经开始动摇了
I think this boy's gone soft on us.

930
01:04:46,400 --> 01:04:48,846
你不接我的电话？
Were you going to ignore my call?

931
01:04:49,000 --> 01:04:52,322
你应该告诉我怀特也会去
You should have told me Wyatt was gonna be there.

932
01:04:52,480 --> 01:04:54,721
你为什么来回的踱步 看上去很紧张
Why do you keep pacing so much? You look nervous.

933
01:04:54,880 --> 01:04:56,609
有什么要说的吗？
You have something you want to tell me?

934
01:05:00,240 --> 01:05:01,651
你在哪？
Where are you?

935
01:05:01,800 --> 01:05:03,723
现在我来解释下一步行动
Now let me explain to you how this is going to work.

936
01:05:03,920 --> 01:05:05,729
我们拿你一个朋友开刀
We hit one of your friends first.

937
01:05:05,920 --> 01:05:07,729
可能是个女性
Or maybe the girl.

938
01:05:07,920 --> 01:05:10,002
如果你敢动她…
If you even touch her...

939
01:05:10,160 --> 01:05:12,891
那就去拿到我们所要的东西
Then get us what we need.

940
01:06:30,000 --> 01:06:32,731
给你两天时间入侵艾康公司
You have two days to break into Eikon.

941
01:06:32,920 --> 01:06:35,969
最后一次警告
This is your last warning.

942
01:07:44,680 --> 01:07:48,207
帮帮我！快来帮帮我
Help! Help me! Somebody help me!

943
01:07:53,080 --> 01:07:57,005
他说我有两天时间 前晚说的
He said I had two days. That was the night before last.

944
01:07:57,160 --> 01:07:59,145
这些人无孔不入
These people are everywhere.

945
01:07:59,145 --> 01:08:00,926
在你家中布满摄像头
Put cameras in your house.

946
01:08:03,640 --> 01:08:06,564
对不起 我只是…
I'm sorry. I just...

947
01:08:08,080 --> 01:08:10,003
我搞砸了 爸爸
I messed up, Dad.

948
01:08:11,680 --> 01:08:14,047
我本以为知道自己在干什么
I thought I knew what I was doing.

949
01:08:23,000 --> 01:08:25,321
你必须自谋生路
You have to figure a way out.

950
01:08:26,440 --> 01:08:27,441
亚当
Adam.

951
01:08:29,120 --> 01:08:30,087
亚当
Adam.

952
01:08:31,160 --> 01:08:33,891
- 亚当！  - 是真的 好吗？
- Adam! - This is serious, OK?

953
01:08:36,680 --> 01:08:38,444
你必须自谋生路
You got to figure a way out.

954
01:08:40,800 --> 01:08:42,290
没那么容易
It's not that easy.

955
01:08:42,440 --> 01:08:46,081
好吗？关心我的人都处于危险之中
OK? I put a lot of people I care about in danger.

956
01:08:52,120 --> 01:08:57,081
亚当 我觉得FBI是唯一的选择
Adam, I think the FBI is the only option.

957
01:09:02,960 --> 01:09:04,928
我会坐牢的
I could go to jail.

958
01:09:06,520 --> 01:09:09,490
不然他们会杀了你
Or they could kill you.

959
01:09:50,440 --> 01:09:52,568
一辆黑车突然窜出来撞倒了他
There was a black car and it just came out of nowhere and it hit him.

960
01:09:52,760 --> 01:09:54,728
慢点 他还好吗？
你在哪儿？
Slow down. Is he all right? Where are you?

961
01:09:54,880 --> 01:09:56,798
我联系了你一整天
I've been trying to reach you all day.

962
01:09:56,798 --> 01:09:58,521
凯文在医院 他还好
Kev's at the hospital, but he's OK.

963
01:09:58,680 --> 01:10:00,330
我猜他们在威胁我们
I think they're discharging us now.

964
01:10:00,480 --> 01:10:02,608
有目击证人吗？有没有看到牌照？
OK, were there witnesses? Did anyone get the plates?

965
01:10:02,800 --> 01:10:04,084
不清楚 不知道
I don't think so. I don't know,

966
01:10:04,084 --> 01:10:05,770
一切来得太快 我得走了
it just all happened so fast. I got to go.

967
01:10:05,920 --> 01:10:07,922
- 记得再电话我  - 我会的
- OK, call me back. - I will.

968
01:10:58,240 --> 01:10:59,969
你什么毛病？！
Hey! What's the matter with you?!

969
01:11:13,200 --> 01:11:15,248
闪开！
Go, go, go, go!

970
01:11:36,000 --> 01:11:37,525
跪下
On your knees.

971
01:11:37,680 --> 01:11:40,081
- 我照做！  - 快跪下！
- I'll do it, I'll do it! - Get on your knees!

972
01:11:42,560 --> 01:11:43,910
你今晚溜进去
You're going in tonight,

973
01:11:43,910 --> 01:11:45,962
你会用到艾玛的手机
and you'll need Emma's phone to do it.

974
01:11:46,920 --> 01:11:48,285
起来干活
Get moving.

975
01:11:52,240 --> 01:11:53,287
我能进来吗？
Can I come in?

976
01:12:03,960 --> 01:12:05,405
我对你不诚实
I haven't been honest with you.

977
01:12:11,720 --> 01:12:13,131
什么意思？
What do you mean?

978
01:12:16,480 --> 01:12:20,041
有些事我没有告诉你
There's things I want to tell you that I haven't told you.

979
01:12:29,400 --> 01:12:30,845
关于什么？
What is it?

980
01:13:52,120 --> 01:13:53,406
坎西迪先生
Mr. Cassidy.

981
01:13:57,720 --> 01:13:59,722
- 怎么  - 这么晚加班？
- Yeah? - Working late tonight?

982
01:14:01,280 --> 01:14:03,044
熬夜燃烧脂肪
Burning that midnight oil.

983
01:14:57,960 --> 01:14:59,121
亚当？
Adam?

984
01:15:24,784 --> 01:15:26,368
（系统关闭）

985
01:15:37,800 --> 01:15:39,370
一到第五层都断电了
I've lost floors one through five.

986
01:15:39,520 --> 01:15:41,841
我们已打开第二区安全灯
We've got security lights in sector two.

987
01:15:42,000 --> 01:15:43,490
坚守岗位
Hold your position.

988
01:15:46,600 --> 01:15:48,728
接通网络管理员的电话
Get our IT guy on the line.

989
01:15:51,520 --> 01:15:53,302
去第三区前
Before we move on to sector three,

990
01:15:53,302 --> 01:15:54,524
检查一下服务器
let's check that server.

991
01:16:04,200 --> 01:16:06,248
我要大楼内所有人的名单
I want the list of everyone in the building.

992
01:16:14,040 --> 01:16:15,041
别动…
Control...

993
01:16:19,400 --> 01:16:21,402
- 只有一笔进出记录  - 是谁？
- I'm only showing one exec present. - Who is it?

994
01:16:21,560 --> 01:16:22,527
亚当·坎西迪
Adam Cassidy.

995
01:16:25,760 --> 01:16:27,046
拜托
Oh, come on.

996
01:16:31,960 --> 01:16:34,167
我是艾玛 请留言
Hi, it's Emma. Leave a message.

997
01:16:44,600 --> 01:16:46,841
马丁 去查一下亚当·坎西迪
Marty, go check on Adam Cassidy.

998
01:16:47,720 --> 01:16:49,609
收到 我去了！
Roger, I'm en route. Come on!

999
01:17:05,849 --> 01:17:09,767
（无法验证）

1000
01:17:21,849 --> 01:17:23,767
（第2次 共3次）

1001
01:17:24,840 --> 01:17:26,763
亚当·坎西迪不在办公室
Adam Cassidy is not in his office.

1002
01:17:26,920 --> 01:17:28,126
妈的
Shit.

1003
01:17:28,920 --> 01:17:32,606
全员追缉 不惜一切手段
All hands on, get this guy! Use any means necessary.

1004
01:17:40,840 --> 01:17:41,841
安全
Clear.

1005
01:17:44,320 --> 01:17:45,606
坎西迪先生！
Mr. Cassidy!

1006
01:18:15,360 --> 01:18:18,204
有人在研发中心密室
We've got somebody at the vault.

1007
01:19:40,358 --> 01:19:44,193
（一日为贼 日日为贼）

1008
01:20:00,160 --> 01:20:01,491
搞什么？
What the hell?

1009
01:20:14,520 --> 01:20:15,521
乔克
Jock.

1010
01:20:17,120 --> 01:20:18,610
坎西迪先生
Mr. Cassidy.

1011
01:20:19,680 --> 01:20:22,445
人赃并获了吧？
Got caught with your hand in the cookie jar, didn't you?

1012
01:20:24,640 --> 01:20:27,610
我… 乔克 我可以解释这一切
I... Jock, I can explain this.

1013
01:20:28,120 --> 01:20:29,531
你打算从哪里开始？
Where you gonna start?

1014
01:20:30,640 --> 01:20:33,291
我真的没想到
I was beginning to think it would never happen.

1015
01:20:34,840 --> 01:20:37,687
怀特宁愿公司倒闭
Wyatt would rather watch his company crumble

1016
01:20:37,687 --> 01:20:38,890
也不肯卖给我
than sell it to me.

1017
01:20:39,840 --> 01:20:43,811
而你则带着野心一同搅局
Then you came along with your blind ambition.

1018
01:20:45,000 --> 01:20:47,480
我们录下了所有的会谈
We recorded it all, every conversation,

1019
01:20:47,680 --> 01:20:49,921
你和怀特的每条信息
every text between you and Wyatt.

1020
01:20:51,120 --> 01:20:54,681
你告诉尼克 让他把公司股份转卖给我
You tell Nick he'll be selling me majority shares in his company

1021
01:20:54,840 --> 01:20:57,730
否则我就把你们互相勾结的证据交给FBI
or evidence of your collusion goes to the FBI.

1022
01:21:00,160 --> 01:21:02,162
你操纵我
You manipulated me.

1023
01:21:02,320 --> 01:21:04,049
是的
Yes.

1024
01:21:05,280 --> 01:21:08,348
明天中午萨顿俱乐部
You'll be at the Sutton Club tomorrow at noon.

1025
01:21:08,348 --> 01:21:09,524
你 尼克 还有我
You, Nick, and me.

1026
01:21:10,440 --> 01:21:13,728
没有外人 不带律师 不带保镖
Nobody else. No lawyers, no handlers. Nobody.

1027
01:21:13,880 --> 01:21:15,245
让他走！
Let him out!

1028
01:21:29,520 --> 01:21:31,329
天大的错误
Big mistake.

1029
01:21:33,960 --> 01:21:35,644
是的
Yeah.

1030
01:22:06,000 --> 01:22:09,083
你怎么来了 你不能呆着
What are you doing here? You can't be here.

1031
01:22:12,360 --> 01:22:13,600
你利用我
You used me.

1032
01:22:13,760 --> 01:22:16,445
很抱歉
I'm sorry. OK? I'm so sorry.

1033
01:22:17,920 --> 01:22:19,285
你必须走 这里不安全
You got to go, you're not safe here.

1034
01:22:19,440 --> 01:22:21,761
每件事…你说的每句话
Everything you... everything you said,

1035
01:22:21,920 --> 01:22:24,295
你做的每件事…
every... everything you did...

1036
01:22:25,128 --> 01:22:26,164
都是撒谎
was a lie.

1037
01:22:26,320 --> 01:22:28,402
不 不全是
No, that's not true. Not everything.

1038
01:22:32,040 --> 01:22:34,042
我想出人头地
I wanted to be someone else.

1039
01:22:39,960 --> 01:22:41,121
你成功了
Now you are.

1040
01:22:44,960 --> 01:22:46,564
你成功了
Now you are.

1041
01:22:48,960 --> 01:22:49,802
你知道…
You know...

1042
01:22:51,760 --> 01:22:54,764
我爱你是因为你的与众不同
I fell for you because you weren't like everyone else.

1043
01:23:00,360 --> 01:23:03,443
艾玛 我会弥补一切的
Emma, I'm gonna make this right.

1044
01:23:05,880 --> 01:23:07,962
你根本不了解局势
You don't know what that is.

1045
01:23:30,000 --> 01:23:32,890
你搞砸了
Well, you sure messed that up.

1046
01:23:33,040 --> 01:23:34,644
我还在想办法 好吗？
Hey, look, I'm trying, OK?

1047
01:23:34,800 --> 01:23:38,327
好了 你的办法完了 我们去兜风
Yeah, well, now you're done trying. Let's go for a ride.

1048
01:23:40,320 --> 01:23:42,243
- 你什么都没有得到吧？  - 都是设计好的陷阱！
- Look, you don't get it, OK? - It was all a setup!

1049
01:23:42,400 --> 01:23:43,970
- 上车！  - 这都是设计好的！
- Get in the car! - It was all a setup!

1050
01:24:24,040 --> 01:24:25,485
对不起 兄弟
I'm sorry, man.

1051
01:24:28,080 --> 01:24:30,321
道什么歉？
What are you sorry for?

1052
01:24:30,480 --> 01:24:32,323
又不是你的撞的我
You didn't run me over, did you?

1053
01:24:33,440 --> 01:24:35,124
都是我的错
I'm the reason for all of this.

1054
01:24:41,000 --> 01:24:42,729
问题是…
The real question is...

1055
01:24:45,160 --> 01:24:47,242
…接下来我们怎么办？
...what are we gonna do about it?

1056
01:24:52,320 --> 01:24:54,322
我会以牙还牙 我…
I'm going to use what they taught me...

1057
01:24:55,720 --> 01:24:57,848
…摧毁他们的帝国
...to destroy what they built.

1058
01:25:08,360 --> 01:25:11,807
和荷兰人交易进展如何？
So, what's the news on the Dutch deal?

1059
01:25:12,000 --> 01:25:14,082
- 不知道  - 他们已经没有价值了
- I don't know. - Good, we won't need them anyway.

1060
01:25:19,120 --> 01:25:21,088
记得没请你啊
Don't remember inviting you.

1061
01:25:22,440 --> 01:25:25,091
我的离职派对会为一切画上句话
My going-away party got this whole thing rolling.

1062
01:25:26,040 --> 01:25:28,964
这可能是我在你们面前最后一次露面
I thought it was only fair that I show up for yours.

1063
01:25:30,920 --> 01:25:32,729
你在说什么？
What are you talking about?

1064
01:25:32,880 --> 01:25:35,087
戈达策划了所有这一切…
Goddard orchestrated this whole thing...

1065
01:25:36,840 --> 01:25:38,968
…诱导你陷入犯罪泥沼
...to entrap you into committing a crime.

1066
01:25:43,080 --> 01:25:44,684
我没有犯罪
I didn't commit a crime.

1067
01:25:46,160 --> 01:25:47,366
是你做的
You did.

1068
01:25:49,160 --> 01:25:51,083
你的帝国就要毁灭了
This is the death of your empire, Nick.

1069
01:25:51,240 --> 01:25:53,971
给你的钱与我无关
And you were funded with money I never touched,

1070
01:25:54,120 --> 01:25:56,559
是一家我从未听过的公司经手的
by corporations I had never heard of.

1071
01:25:56,559 --> 01:25:57,522
那家公司一分不值
He has nothing.

1072
01:25:57,680 --> 01:25:59,523
你错了 他掌控一切
He has everything.

1073
01:25:59,680 --> 01:26:01,144
电邮 短信
E-mails, texts.

1074
01:26:01,144 --> 01:26:03,890
还破解了摄像头
He got the break-in on camera.

1075
01:26:04,760 --> 01:26:06,213
所有的线索都指向你
All the dots connect back to you.

1076
01:26:06,213 --> 01:26:07,411
整个事情都是设计好的
The whole thing was a setup.

1077
01:26:07,560 --> 01:26:09,050
怎么回事？怎么回事？
What's going on? What's going on?

1078
01:26:09,200 --> 01:26:11,224
我们自有周详！
We had good intel on this!

1079
01:26:11,224 --> 01:26:13,808
你何谈周详 尼克？
Where did you get that intel, Nick?

1080
01:26:25,120 --> 01:26:26,770
别荒谬了
This is absurd.

1081
01:26:42,200 --> 01:26:43,850
你不能…
You can't just...

1082
01:26:47,920 --> 01:26:49,081
汉米尔顿
Hamilton.

1083
01:26:50,840 --> 01:26:52,842
乔克的老家
Jack's hometown.

1084
01:26:56,800 --> 01:26:58,006
尼克…
Nick...

1085
01:27:13,640 --> 01:27:14,846
米彻姆
Meachum.

1086
01:27:30,240 --> 01:27:31,844
解决一个
That's one down.

1087
01:27:34,000 --> 01:27:35,240
还有一个
One more to go.

1088
01:27:45,840 --> 01:27:47,808
不管你用什么招 最好管用
Whatever you have better be good.

1089
01:27:47,960 --> 01:27:50,088
如果奏效 我们都撤退比较保险
If it works, we both walk away with an insurance policy

1090
01:27:50,280 --> 01:27:52,123
再多的钱都也买不来
no amount of money can buy.

1091
01:27:52,280 --> 01:27:54,567
万一不奏效呢？
Yeah, but if it doesn't?

1092
01:28:10,480 --> 01:28:12,363
拿出手机 请坐
Get out your phones. Sit down.

1093
01:28:12,363 --> 01:28:14,246
扣出电池放在桌上
Put the batteries on the table.

1094
01:28:41,160 --> 01:28:43,242
它说你有备机
It says you've got another phone.

1095
01:29:09,520 --> 01:29:11,727
- 不 不  - 怎么了？
- Oh, no, no. - What happened?

1096
01:29:11,880 --> 01:29:13,325
信号丢失 两部都没了
I lost the signal. Both phones, they're gone.

1097
01:29:13,480 --> 01:29:14,641
能找回来吗？
Can you get it back?

1098
01:29:21,240 --> 01:29:24,687
- 你必须出价  - 我会付钱的
- You'll pay for this. - Yeah, I'll pay.

1099
01:29:26,320 --> 01:29:30,644
我买下你怀特公司该死的全部股权
I'm buying every goddamn share of Wyatt Corporation's stock you own,

1100
01:29:30,840 --> 01:29:33,161
只需40%的钱
and I'm paying 40 cents on the dollar.

1101
01:29:34,760 --> 01:29:36,285
意下如何？
How does that sound?

1102
01:29:39,640 --> 01:29:41,722
即便我不收购你 联邦政府也会收购你
I get it or the Feds do.

1103
01:29:45,960 --> 01:29:48,201
- 你不会得逞的  - 闭嘴 亚当
- You'll never get away with this. - Shut up, Adam.

1104
01:29:48,400 --> 01:29:51,882
你不过是个方便的工具 绣花枕头
You're nothing but a convenient tool, an empty vessel.

1105
01:29:52,040 --> 01:29:53,326
我塞你一嘴屎尿
I filled you with piss and vinegar

1106
01:29:53,480 --> 01:29:57,007
告诉你这是香槟 你一样舔得干干净净
and told you it was champagne and you lapped it up.

1107
01:29:58,800 --> 01:30:01,406
- 我不会签字的  - 那你等着坐牢
- I'm not signing this. - Then you'll go to jail.

1108
01:30:02,680 --> 01:30:05,684
凭什么？ 你有什么王牌？！
With what? What have you got?!

1109
01:30:11,080 --> 01:30:12,127
什么？
What?

1110
01:30:12,280 --> 01:30:14,965
- 赶紧签！  - 你已经很得势了
- Sign it! - You have taken credit for everything.

1111
01:30:15,120 --> 01:30:17,272
你什么都没有创造过！
And you've created nothing!

1112
01:30:17,272 --> 01:30:18,886
你这个自大的混蛋！
You arrogant bastard!

1113
01:30:19,480 --> 01:30:22,245
我把一件被众人耻笑的砖头设备…
I took a brick device that everybody laughed at

1114
01:30:22,400 --> 01:30:26,246
最终变成人类寸步不离的宝贝
and turned it into the one thing that no one can do without.

1115
01:30:26,440 --> 01:30:28,169
我的自大是我自己挣来的！
I earned my arrogance!

1116
01:30:28,360 --> 01:30:30,784
是的！但没有我什么都不会发生
Yes, and none of that happens without me!

1117
01:30:30,784 --> 01:30:32,285
你是站在我肩膀上！
You stood on my shoulders!

1118
01:30:32,440 --> 01:30:34,568
现在我站在你的脖子上！
And now I'm standing on your neck!

1119
01:30:35,960 --> 01:30:38,611
我始终比你棋高一着 尼克
I'm 15 moves ahead of you, Nick.

1120
01:30:38,760 --> 01:30:41,286
荷兰人也给我报价了！
The Dutch offer, me!

1121
01:30:41,440 --> 01:30:45,446
我一直没能收紧圈套 直到…
I strung you along until the only hope was...

1122
01:30:45,612 --> 01:30:46,731
亚当的出现
Adam.

1123
01:30:50,440 --> 01:30:52,283
这不可能
That's impossible.

1124
01:30:52,440 --> 01:30:53,885
不可能？
Impossible?

1125
01:30:54,040 --> 01:30:57,010
我建立了怀特公司
I built Wyatt Corp.

1126
01:30:57,160 --> 01:31:00,767
卖不卖 你的公司都完蛋了
Sell or not, your company is finished.

1127
01:31:00,920 --> 01:31:03,969
你没有稻草绳可抓了 即便有
You've got nothing in the pipe, and even if you did,

1128
01:31:04,120 --> 01:31:07,488
你也没有资金投放市场
you've got no money to market it with.

1129
01:31:07,640 --> 01:31:11,281
40%的股份 总比坐牢好吧
Forty cents on the dollar is a lot better than jail.

1130
01:31:11,480 --> 01:31:12,845
你自行决定
You make the choice.

1131
01:31:37,200 --> 01:31:38,326
现在滚
Now get out.

1132
01:31:41,480 --> 01:31:43,403
他喜欢干掉自己的年轻一辈
He likes to eat his young.

1133
01:31:45,680 --> 01:31:47,489
那也是我的自由
They're mine to eat.

1134
01:32:05,520 --> 01:32:09,411
该回去过你原本的悲惨生活了
It's time to go back to your sad little life.

1135
01:32:10,120 --> 01:32:11,531
何必大费周章？
Why go to all the trouble?

1136
01:32:12,920 --> 01:32:15,571
因为我想看到他头破血流 你走吧
Because I wanted to see him bleed. Go.

1137
01:32:15,720 --> 01:32:16,729
不 远非如此
No. There's more to it,

1138
01:32:16,729 --> 01:32:18,371
你没必要出此险招的
you wouldn't risk it all just for that.

1139
01:32:18,520 --> 01:32:20,128
我说过 亚当
I told you, Adam,

1140
01:32:20,128 --> 01:32:22,809
竞争激发创新
competition breeds innovation.

1141
01:32:22,960 --> 01:32:25,361
他在公司混得有模有样后 私欲膨胀
With his name on the door, he developed his ass off.

1142
01:32:25,560 --> 01:32:27,369
你需要他
You needed him.

1143
01:32:27,560 --> 01:32:29,722
你需要他的创造力 因为他比你聪明
You needed his mind because he was smarter than you.

1144
01:32:29,920 --> 01:32:32,526
他把一片伟大的处理器用在一部屎样的手机上
He made a great processor and a shitty phone

1145
01:32:32,680 --> 01:32:35,524
他该落得和你一样的下场 走吧
and he served a purpose, just like you did. Go.

1146
01:32:37,400 --> 01:32:39,004
没有他你什么都干不了
You're nothing without him.

1147
01:32:40,560 --> 01:32:43,723
Occura是真的 我说到做到
Occura is real. It'll do everything I said it would.

1148
01:32:44,560 --> 01:32:46,688
我不过是需要他的处理器而已
I just needed his processor to run it.

1149
01:33:00,560 --> 01:33:02,289
- 谁？  - 戈达先生？
- Who is this? - Mr. Goddard?

1150
01:33:02,440 --> 01:33:04,329
是谁？
Who is this?

1151
01:33:05,520 --> 01:33:08,000
你真应该彻底删除你收到的电邮
You should really trash your e-mails when you're done reading them.

1152
01:33:11,600 --> 01:33:13,090
早上我给所有人发了邮件
I sent you all an e-mail this morning

1153
01:33:13,280 --> 01:33:16,124
内含类3DPS身份鉴别数据
in which I encoded 3DPS-like data to identify you.

1154
01:33:20,600 --> 01:33:22,762
有人一直在偷听 乔克
Someone is always listening, Jock.

1155
01:33:22,920 --> 01:33:24,445
一直
Always.

1156
01:33:53,520 --> 01:33:54,681
戈达先生
Mr. Goddard.

1157
01:33:54,840 --> 01:33:56,524
戈达先生 你被捕了
Mr. Goddard, you're under arrest.

1158
01:33:56,680 --> 01:34:00,207
我会让你生不如死
I'm gonna make your life a living hell.

1159
01:34:00,400 --> 01:34:02,289
站起来 手放背后
Please stand, place your hands behind your back.

1160
01:34:03,640 --> 01:34:05,608
我们逮到他了
Yes! We got him.

1161
01:34:07,760 --> 01:34:10,286
你们做了一件大好事儿 孩子
You did the right thing, kid.

1162
01:34:10,440 --> 01:34:12,283
现在指控你重罪欺诈
The charges against you include felony fraud,

1163
01:34:12,440 --> 01:34:14,094
商业间谍罪
industrial espionage,

1164
01:34:14,094 --> 01:34:15,452
妨碍司法
obstruction of justice,

1165
01:34:15,452 --> 01:34:17,002
及内幕交易
insider trading.

1166
01:34:17,160 --> 01:34:20,369
奥古斯丁·戈达 你有权保持沉默
Augustine Goddard, you have the right to remain silent.

1167
01:34:20,520 --> 01:34:23,444
但你所说的一切都将成为呈堂证供
Anything you say can and will be used in a court of law.

1168
01:34:24,640 --> 01:34:26,483
你有权请律师
You have the right to an attorney.

1169
01:34:26,680 --> 01:34:28,513
如果你请不起律师
If you cannot afford an attorney,

1170
01:34:28,513 --> 01:34:30,401
法院也会为你指派一名律师
the court will appoint one for you.

1171
01:34:30,600 --> 01:34:32,762
听懂我宣读的你的权利了？
Do you understand these rights as I have read them to you?

1172
01:34:39,840 --> 01:34:41,922
我向FBI举报了怀特和戈达
I handed the Feds Wyatt and Goddard.

1173
01:34:43,680 --> 01:34:46,286
他们将有段日子看不到阳光了
They won't be seeing light for a very long time.

1174
01:34:47,520 --> 01:34:50,285
朱迪斯和米彻姆罪有应得
Judith and Meachum got what they deserved too.

1175
01:34:52,680 --> 01:34:55,524
而我很幸运
As for me, I got lucky.

1176
01:34:55,680 --> 01:34:58,206
因为我的合作 所以联邦调查局放我一马
The Feds cut me a break for my cooperation.

1177
01:34:58,680 --> 01:34:59,647
不…
No...

1178
01:35:08,720 --> 01:35:12,088
曾经的追求现在想来其实也没那么重要
The things I thought I wanted don't seem so important anymore.

1179
01:35:14,160 --> 01:35:15,685
吃一堑长一智 还有…
I do know right from wrong, and...

1180
01:35:17,480 --> 01:35:20,131
…隔了这么久才能做回我自己
...I'm sorry it took me so long to act on it.

1181
01:35:21,960 --> 01:35:25,009
我只想你知道
I just want you to know that

1182
01:35:25,160 --> 01:35:27,401
我从不曾想对不起你
I never wanted to do any of this to you.

1183
01:35:30,400 --> 01:35:32,402
希望有一天我能弥补一切
I hope one day I can make things right.

1184
01:35:38,440 --> 01:35:39,680
对不起 艾玛
I'm sorry, Emma.

1185
01:35:51,760 --> 01:35:52,966
谢谢
Thanks.

1186
01:35:54,760 --> 01:35:56,842
快！快！快！快！
Go, go, go, go! Go! Go! Go!

1187
01:35:57,080 --> 01:35:58,923
快跑 快跑！
Run, run!

1188
01:36:05,520 --> 01:36:06,567
干嘛？
What?

1189
01:36:09,760 --> 01:36:12,411
我有说你是对的吗？
Did I ever tell you, you were right?

1190
01:36:13,760 --> 01:36:15,125
关于什么？
About what?

1191
01:36:16,160 --> 01:36:17,491
一切
Everything.

1192
01:36:21,560 --> 01:36:23,244
真心的
I mean that.

1193
01:36:23,400 --> 01:36:25,289
抱歉我以前没有听你的
I'm sorry I didn't listen to you.

1194
01:36:41,240 --> 01:36:43,083
和那女孩发展的怎么样了？
How's it going with that girl?

1195
01:36:45,560 --> 01:36:46,971
她不愿意和我说话
Well, she won't talk to me.

1196
01:36:48,680 --> 01:36:50,762
塞翁失马焉知非福
It ain't over till it's over.

1197
01:36:51,920 --> 01:36:55,561
知道我约你妈出来约了多久吗？
You know how long it took me to get a date with your mother?

1198
01:36:56,520 --> 01:36:57,760
多久？
How long?

1199
01:37:00,680 --> 01:37:02,762
花儿都谢了
A long time.

1200
01:37:04,960 --> 01:37:08,123
我那时比你现在还帅
And I was much better-looking then than you are now.

1201
01:37:08,280 --> 01:37:11,090
- 真的吗？  - 噢耶
- Oh, is that right? - Oh, yeah. Oh, yeah.

1202
01:37:19,280 --> 01:37:22,489
你去哪儿？地铁在这边
Where you going? The subway is this way.

1203
01:37:22,640 --> 01:37:24,927
我有更快的交通工具 过来
I got a faster ride. Come on.

1204
01:37:31,840 --> 01:37:33,683
我以为这事情已经了结了呢？
I thought we were done with this shit?

1205
01:37:33,840 --> 01:37:35,808
租的啦 老爸 我租了一天
It's a rental, Dad. I got it for the day.

1206
01:37:35,960 --> 01:37:38,964
哦 真的吗？好啦 让我们找点乐子去
Oh, yeah? Well, then, let's have some fun.

1207
01:37:40,080 --> 01:37:42,845
不迷失自己的方法就是…
One way to remember who you are...

1208
01:37:43,040 --> 01:37:45,407
咋开门的？
How do you open this thing?

1209
01:37:45,560 --> 01:37:47,847
树立正确的英雄榜样
...is to remember who your heroes are.

1210
01:38:00,360 --> 01:38:02,283
我现在自己干
I'm doing things my way now.

1211
01:38:02,480 --> 01:38:05,165
万丈高楼平地起
Building from the ground up.

1212
01:38:05,320 --> 01:38:07,482
万事无捷径
There are no shortcuts.

1213
01:38:08,040 --> 01:38:09,804
我的天呀 你在搞什么？
Oh my God, what are you doing?

1214
01:38:09,960 --> 01:38:12,122
- 啥？我弄混了  - 我们有好多事儿要忙
- What? I messed it up. - We have a lot of things to do.

1215
01:38:12,320 --> 01:38:13,970
- 来吧！  - 好吧 好吧！
- Come on! - All right, Jesus!

1216
01:38:17,880 --> 01:38:19,120
嗨 艾玛
Hi. Emma Jennings.

1217
01:38:19,280 --> 01:38:21,044
稍等
One second.

1218
01:38:23,240 --> 01:38:25,607
亚当有客人
Adam, you have a visitor.

1219
01:38:39,920 --> 01:38:41,365
你好
Hi.

1220
01:38:44,480 --> 01:38:47,165
这地方不错
Nice place you have here.

1221
01:38:47,320 --> 01:38:49,243
我意思是指在布鲁克林区
I mean, for Brooklyn.

1222
01:38:51,040 --> 01:38:53,168
非常荣幸你能来
I'm glad you came.

1223
01:38:53,360 --> 01:38:56,967
一直收到一家新公司的职位邀请电邮
Kept getting e-mails about a job offer at a brand-new startup company.

1224
01:38:58,800 --> 01:39:00,404
为什么我没看见…
Why I didn't see that coming...

1225
01:39:00,560 --> 01:39:03,723
我们…
Yeah, we, uh...

1226
01:39:03,880 --> 01:39:06,281
我们真的需要你
We really need you here.

1227
01:39:06,960 --> 01:39:08,450
你们请不起我的
You couldn't afford me.

1228
01:39:08,600 --> 01:39:10,921
算你公司股份
Lots of stock options.

1229
01:39:14,080 --> 01:39:16,082
那你得更加把劲
You have to do better than that.

1230
01:39:18,960 --> 01:39:20,405
好
OK.

1231
01:39:25,680 --> 01:39:27,921
我真的需要你
I need you here.

1232
01:39:39,440 --> 01:39:40,930
我考虑考虑
I'll think about it.

1233
01:39:52,720 --> 01:39:53,846
走 我请你喝一杯
Come on, let me buy you a drink.

1234
01:39:54,000 --> 01:39:55,843
你说你喜欢桥那边的人的
You said you had a thing for bridge-and-tunnel.

1235
01:39:56,000 --> 01:39:58,128
这是你原话 艾玛
Your words. Emma.

1236
01:40:01,040 --> 01:40:03,725
那至少让我感谢一下你的大驾光临？
Can I at least thank you for considering my offer?

1237
01:40:29,880 --> 01:40:31,006
谢谢
Thank you.

1238
01:40:35,320 --> 01:40:37,561
我喜欢经过那大桥
I like being across the bridge.

1239
01:40:38,360 --> 01:40:41,887
那里才有家的感觉
Over here, it feels like home.

1240
01:40:58,125 --> 01:41:00,360
谢谢观影
